{
  "text": "We choose the finite space H f according to the construction of the noncommutative Standard Model [CITATION_1] , dimH f = 96 and \u2207 H f is the appropriate covariant derivative associated to the Standard Model gauge group U (1) Y \u00d7 SU (2) \u03c9 \u00d7 SU (3) c . We know that (for related notations see [HPS] , [IKS] ),",
